Peggie Castle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peggie_Castle 0 Peggie Castle (December 22, 1927 – August 11, 1973) was an American actress who specialized in playing the "other woman" in B-movies. She was also billed under the names Peggy Castle and Peggie Call.
